# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><table><tgroup><tbody><row><entry>
#: debian-reference.en.xml:3486
msgid "Redirect standard input of <literal>command</literal> to the following lines until \"<literal>delimiter</literal>\" is met.  The leading tab characters are stripped from input lines. (Here documents)"
