#: debian-reference.en.xml:5445
msgid "The \"<literal>aptitude why &lt;regex&gt;</literal>\" can list more information by \"<literal>aptitude -v why &lt;regex&gt;</literal>\".  Similar information can be obtained by \"<literal>apt-cache rdepends &lt;package&gt;</literal>\"."
