# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xml:8971
msgid "The name of device nodes can be configured by files in \"<literal>/etc/udev/rules.d/</literal>\" (see \"<literal>/usr/share/doc/udev/writing_udev_rules/index.html</literal>\")."
