# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xml:18055
msgid "to set the system wide default locale value in the \"<literal>/etc/defaults/locale</literal>\" for use by PAM (see <xref linkend=\"_pam_and_nss\"/>)."
