# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xml:18133
msgid "For example, you can obtain the localized message for manpage by installing the <literal>manpages-&lt;LANG&gt;</literal> package. To read the Italian-language manpage for &lt;programname&gt;, execute"
